### Login to get token
# @name login
POST http://localhost:8080/abtechzone/auth/log-in
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin"
}

###

@token = {{login.response.body.result.token}}

### 1. Add item to cart (new item)
# @name addToCart
POST http://localhost:8080/abtechzone/cart/add
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "productSkuId": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}

### 2. Add same item again (should accumulate quantity)
POST http://localhost:8080/abtechzone/cart/add
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "productSkuId": 1,
  "quantity": 3
}

### 3. Add a different SKU to cart
POST http://localhost:8080/abtechzone/cart/add
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "productSkuId": 2,
  "quantity": 1
}

### 4. Get cart
GET http://localhost:8080/abtechzone/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Update cart item quantity
PATCH http://localhost:8080/abtechzone/cart/items/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "quantity": 10
}

### 6. Update cart item quantity (exceed stock → should fail)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/abtechzone/cart/items/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "quantity": 99999
}

### 7. Update cart item quantity (invalid → should fail validation)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/abtechzone/cart/items/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "quantity": 0
}

### 8. Remove a single item from cart
DELETE http://localhost:8080/abtechzone/cart/items/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Remove non-existent item (should fail)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/abtechzone/cart/items/999999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Clear entire cart
DELETE http://localhost:8080/abtechzone/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Get cart after clear (should be empty or not found)
GET http://localhost:8080/abtechzone/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Add item with non-existent SKU (should fail)
POST http://localhost:8080/abtechzone/cart/add
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "productSkuId": 999999,
  "quantity": 1
}

### 13. Access cart without token (should 401)
GET http://localhost:8080/abtechzone/cart
